&lt;p&gt;Flow Traders is looking for a new Senior Operations Specialist to join our Operations department. This is a unique opportunity to join a leading proprietary trading firm with an entrepreneurial and innovative culture at the heart of its business.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will join the Flow Traders EMEA Operations team based in our Amsterdam office. We have an expanding product universe, covering all major asset classes. Our team covers a multitude of areas and follows the full trade lifecycle. As such, the opportunities to learn and grow are limitless within the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For this role, we are looking for candidates with 5+ years of relevant experience in Operations, Middle Office, or a related field, combined with good analytical and programing skills, as well as a a strong desire to continue learning and developing within this space. If you are interested in the role and believe your experience aligns, we encourage you to apply and include a short explanation of your motivation to join Flow Traders.&lt;/p&gt;
