&lt;li&gt;A degree in Finance, Economics, Mathematics, or something similarly quantitative&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Python and SQL are hard requirements - you write code, not just read it&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sharp attention to detail and a genuine appetite for getting into the weeds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior exposure to trading, front office, or technology teams is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable handling large, messy datasets and knowing when the numbers don&#39;t add up&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You reach for a script before you reach for a spreadsheet&lt;/li&gt;
