&lt;li data-uuid=&quot;8ff379a5-033c-47e2-b703-c2f31929aba1&quot;&gt;Partner with Quantitative Researchers to conduct research: test hypotheses and tune/develop data-driven systematic trading strategies and alpha signals&lt;/li&gt;
